<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17298</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>星期六一大早，凯蒂和妈妈走进了拼克药店。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17298</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂戴着组长帽，拿着希金斯老师的清单。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她们在过道里走来走去，寻找龙卷风避难所需要的物品。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“急救霜。”凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38104</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“找到了！”妈妈边说边把软膏放到购物筐里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38104</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41104</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“绷带和胶带。”凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41104</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“绷带和胶带！”妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂看着她的清单。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有一样东西。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54351</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们需要一个盒子来装所有的东西。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54351</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58155</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈用手指着一个高架子上方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58155</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这有一个大小正合适！”她大喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62251</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65251</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太好了！”凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65251</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“合作愉快！”妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73577</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“早上好，戴布拉。你好，凯蒂。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73577</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拼克太太在收银台说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们都买什么了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83667</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“凯蒂和我正在做急救箱。”妈妈解释道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83667</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88419</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们准备迎接龙卷风季节。”凯蒂说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91419</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望您家已经准备好了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97422</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拼克太太笑了，把她们的东西放进了妈妈的包里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97422</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当凯蒂和妈妈走出药店时，她们听到了一个熟悉的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“凯蒂！戴布拉姨妈！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106169</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108670</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂看着街对面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108670</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111921</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是卢克。”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111921</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卢克坐在沙莉姨妈“脆皮派天堂”咖啡店前的一张桌子旁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118668</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122670</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他在商店窗户上贴了一张纸：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122670</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124042</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>活诱饵</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124042</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125699</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一打湿蚯蚓</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125699</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127067</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一美元</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127067</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133567</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卢克把手伸进一大盆冰里， 从里面拿出一个塑料杯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133567</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你想要一些蚯蚓吗？”他笑着问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140448</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起。”凯蒂说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140448</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们已经吃过了。哈！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看了看冰盆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145517</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150019</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望你有足够的蚯蚓。”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150019</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153529</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我现在没有时间做诱饵生意。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153529</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158519</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我是多诺万龙卷风安全小组的组长。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158519</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163769</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，我全忘了。”卢克皱着眉头说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163769</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那你不再帮我挖蚯蚓了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172017</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，沙莉姨妈推开了咖啡店门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172017</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177090</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>外面空气中弥漫着派和新鲜咖啡的香味。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177090</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“早上好！”她大喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>沙莉姨妈是妈妈的妹妹。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188467</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“老师让我们每个家庭为龙卷风季节做好准备。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188467</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192365</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是卢克忘了。”凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192365</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197391</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> 沙莉姨妈一边笑，一边把围裙上的面粉擦掉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197391</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202117</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她说：“我想如果龙卷风来了，我们会被吹走了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204867</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈和卢克也笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204867</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207867</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂皱着眉头摇了摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207867</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她是唯一一个认真对待这件事的人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219122</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>与此同时，乔伊和爸爸在多诺万池塘上方的山坡上看着树。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219122</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222869</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们刚在两棵榆树停下了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222869</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226869</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这两棵树也许可以。”爸爸说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226869</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229619</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们看看它们相距多远。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229619</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233619</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他从工具带上拿下一个卷尺。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233619</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在这儿，你把卷尺的一端放在这棵树上。”他对乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239369</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245371</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他走向另一棵树，一边走一边拉着卷尺。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245371</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>”一米二。刚好。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254372</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是一个非常适合树屋的地方。”乔伊说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254372</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“从这里，我们可以看到池塘、房子、鸡圈......</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260869</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所有的一切！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260869</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265621</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这两棵树会支撑住树屋的后面。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265621</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268869</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要用两个柱子支撑前面。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268869</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275370</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊转向房子，看见凯蒂和麦古在朝山上跑过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275370</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278872</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“凯蒂和妈妈回来了。”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278872</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282370</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我在路上看见你了。”凯蒂叫道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282370</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你要在这里盖树屋吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285120</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是一个完美的地方，是吧？”乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂点了点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里棒极了。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299628</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可以看到暴风云从西南方向滚滚而来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>299628</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304156</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你知道，龙卷风就是从那里来的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304156</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她抬头朝晴朗的天空望去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>307153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310231</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“干得漂亮，我的团队。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>310231</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她说，然后朝山下跑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>314302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们最好快点开始。”爸爸说</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>78</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>318054</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>322305</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没错， 搭档！”乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>